01  WS-AREA. 
05  WS-VAR1 PIC 9(5) VALUE 12345. 
05  WS-VAR2 PIC 9(5) VALUE 0. 
05  WS-DIVISOR PIC 9(5). 
05  WS-RESULT PIC 9(5). 
05  WS-ERROR-FLAG PIC 9 VALUE 0. 

PROCEDURE DIVISION. 
    MOVE 0 TO WS-DIVISOR 
    IF WS-DIVISOR = 0 THEN 
       MOVE 1 TO WS-ERROR-FLAG 
       DISPLAY "Division by zero detected!" 
    ELSE 
       COMPUTE WS-RESULT = WS-VAR1 / WS-DIVISOR 
       DISPLAY "Result: " WS-RESULT 
    END-IF 
    STOP RUN.